{"tid":1851097,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際特赦組織促建立完全獨立的機制調查警方","createTime":"2020-01-30T01:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T04:57:35.000Z","uid":14918,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6793a6052eaef7ec53f506b5c2622166dc6e70f1","tid":1851097,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:43:30.000Z","msg":"國際特赦組織促建立完全獨立的機制調查警方<br />\n9小時前<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378558&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rFHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=1f8072d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378558&h=9f322719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378558</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】國際特赦組織發表2019年亞洲人權報告，指香港人權迅速惡化，建議政府建立完全獨立的機制，調查警方行為。<br />\n<br />\n報告分析25個國家及地區的人權狀況，其中香港的章節提到，去年香港人權狀況迅速惡化，香港政府跟隨中國內地模糊不清的國家安全定義，進一步蠶食港人和平集會、表達及結社自由，香港警方在遊行中使用過分武力，危險地使用橡膠子彈及布袋彈，毆打未有反抗的示威者等等。<br />\n<br />\n組織亦紀錄了當局任意拘捕的情況，<span style=\"color: red;\">有證據顯示，被捕人士遭酷刑及其他形式的虐待情況，反映執法時有明顯報復心態</span>，建議政府建立完全獨立的機制，調查警方行為。"},{"pid":"f5c6bf06b05b5ec6e12c8198879cf8e6554531cd","tid":1851097,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qMYub9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qMYub9.gif&h=bc3ca129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4f9d0e361875431188b177abbc8587900ad4cdd","tid":1851097,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗疫保命<br />\n推翻暴政</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3fe82301c8ddee3fedd834bcfd5570dfbcc60c89","tid":1851097,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"講真